Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.62,0:00:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小鈴  公子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.21,0:00:13.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.79,0:00:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在春天成為島上居民的梅梅和河童遠野先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後決定住在我們家附近的水車屋裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.40,0:00:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 梅梅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.11,0:00:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  到田裡去給我們去拿蔬菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.09,0:00:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠野先生也一起的  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那烏龜真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.91,0:00:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…都說了遠野先生是河童了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.98,0:00:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才叫我了?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.33,0:00:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.71,0:00:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.00,0:00:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.82,0:00:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:00:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.65,0:01:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:47.95,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望改正…梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:52.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…你確實是新島民梅梅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.47,0:02:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那個怪異的裝束是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:02:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…把…蔬…菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:02:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等下再來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.33,0:03:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.62,0:03:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天開始這裡就是梅梅的家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不夠的東西等下再去拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…果然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍有點吵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事…只是感動得說不出話來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前的風餐露宿相比的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂流到島上之後一直在北邊森林生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都很害羞  一直在逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.52,0:04:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是老是被有兩根尾巴的老虎追趕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這裡是天國
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對遠野先生來說也是個好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童是需要水的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說不是河童是烏龜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人很頑固呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是頑固  是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪怎麼可能存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是龜甲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  梅梅為何會跟遠野先生一起旅行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…這是無論傾聽還是訴說都是充滿淚水的悲傷故事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是紙畫劇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺在…哪裡看到過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:51.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（東映的作品都會有這個標誌 所以行人才說見到過）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天爸爸做了咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大介最喜歡吃咖喱了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能交到一百個朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像之前所說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了克服害羞心理開始獨自旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那某一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnzhunyuan\fs30}其實遠野先生以前扮成壯鰤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:18.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnzhunyuan}（日本對長約60cm的鰤魚的稱呼）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被某條河邊小廟的和尚所封印
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.99,0:06:26.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得它很可憐  將費力建造的封印給解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:33.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  過去記憶中的河已經不再適合河童居住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去尋找清澈的河和伙伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後請多照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏龜的報恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦島太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:20.39,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（御伽草子的主人公，浦島太郎與海龜化身的美女一起去了龍宮，\N歸來後因打開百寶箱而變成白髮老人）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後梅梅被帶到龍宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼淚停不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下水抓不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍋子還有砧板再加上些盤子會更方便點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不夠的東西等下去拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過不能一直給他們添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛就還差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:15.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話就稍稍感覺不害羞了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想自己一個人去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才戴著面具嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能一直都依賴行人和小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到這個地步
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:08:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到要與人相見就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.86,0:09:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也很擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜…拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前見過面的人也許不會很緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是玲的家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是島上唯一的一群木工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從掏耳勺到房屋什麼都能建造的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.59,0:09:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修好了我和遠野先生的家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.39,0:09:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得好好道謝才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:44.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螞…蟻?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.11,0:10:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5  6  7  8  9  10
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.09,0:10:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螞蟻有10隻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:06.59,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（蟻がとお與謝謝ありがとう發音一樣）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…說修房子的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  我做的櫃子如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很容易打開  很方便
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似東西還是不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真高興  第一次被這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都說我的作品沒有任何用處
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了  正好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做的鍋子和盤子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.69,0:10:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請盡情拿去用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:46.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是把需要的東西拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:10:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那能用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用吧  大概
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼高興  是拒絕不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.63,0:11:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅  下午好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅是機會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.18,0:11:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼雪乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下…午…好…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是熊呢  和我…聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是…拜託…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要穿玩偶裝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話能冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊可冷靜不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.92,0:12:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然知道你很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也太不自然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃和企鵝很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是千影小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千影小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.74,0:12:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千影小姐是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是旗袍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面是迷你裙  後面是長裙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這會成為島上流行趨勢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千影小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,stop…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的島民?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嫁禍給我的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:00.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幫忙找犯人在這裡睡懶覺的到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是想起來就火大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才真是慘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從島外來的叫梅梅的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是行人大人的鄰居
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是怎麼樣的新人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我相比肯定是望塵莫及的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺忘了把什麼重要的事情告訴綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.06,0:14:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是個新來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真囂張
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠慘的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千影小姐平時是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾看到島外的東西會改變性格的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼芽該趁早拔除
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果我和誰都沒有好好的交流
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢加油就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…真的能在生活下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭這樣的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太在意比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…我無論如何也想改變
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:14:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅被人看到會很害羞所以要變裝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.29,0:15:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是新人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.17,0:15:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再做小偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.96,0:15:17.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小偷?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概把綾音錯當成麻知姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是追趕梅梅的那個人的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我同那相貌粗暴的姐姐不同  被稱為島上最端莊美麗 賢惠的美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:36.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在說誰…說得這麼出神入化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是綾音的妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊  真失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個  剛才的話聽起來是個可悲的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.16,0:15:46.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然討厭自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  綾音就不想改變自己嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是無稽之談  行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:58.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我最喜歡自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:01.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是做了蠢事還是做了丟人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我也認為自己很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說回來  今天的晚飯是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  還沒決定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 比起改正那害羞的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必須要做的事情難道不是讓自己喜歡上自己嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…要喜歡上…自己?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.87,0:16:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我喜歡上的自己會有什麼優點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問剛見面的我  怎麼可能會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許正如綾音所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算保持現在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅也是有優點的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.51,0:16:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有敢於一人旅行的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫畫也很擅長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我找朋友這點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.52,0:16:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也找到你的優點了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:17:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很中意你那害羞到令人發笑的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  只要喜歡上自己  對自己有信心的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然就會治好害羞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島上有這種動物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:23.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和梅梅一起漂流到島上的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是烏龜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏龜?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.95,0:17:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏龜會叫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏龜會吃黃瓜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  是河童
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是河童遠野先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了河童什麼是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人果然還是頑固啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河…河童?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:17:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭河童
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾音怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得以前綾音被河童襲擊過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  遠野先生請等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.96,0:18:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我  請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠野先生  請等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說…請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.37,0:18:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了…別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.44,0:18:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.43,0:18:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.58,0:19:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾音是懸崖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不停下的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾音…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾音  梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.78,0:19:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾音  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:37.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人大人  再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾音快回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個的話我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.96,0:19:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  遠野先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童的話在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.01,0:19:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我為了讓綾音嚇一跳的變裝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做這種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為看到綾音吃驚的樣子很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.37,0:20:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 全部是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:29.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.69,0:20:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就做了旗袍  想讓你們看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅  這是真的熊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊也許比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一齊打招呼的話  梅梅會嚇一跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家為了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.90,0:20:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅是這裡的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後不管發生什麼都要開開心心地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:05.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝…還有對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回禮什麼的不要客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,800)}{\an9\fs20\bord3\4a&HFF}\N\N{\1c&HC43A2C\3c&HFFFFFF}次回　　　　　　　　{\fs10}\N\N{\fs20}「去贏得  王之寶座」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.98,0:23:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東部的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.96,0:23:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來我們南部的森林裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.66,0:23:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害羞啊
